{"tid":38981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女警涉超市高買下周三開審","createTime":"2016-12-14T09:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T22:58:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20d19a38b3e45cc600cd4de0a037efffa6a98d7b","tid":38981,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"49歲現役女警涉嫌在超市偷竊防蚊貼、XO醬及喉片等總值234元財物，被控盜竊罪。案件今在觀塘法院再提堂，女警否認控罪，控方指超市保安目擊被告犯案，女警遭揭發後辯稱身體不適及服了藥物。裁判官將案件定於本月21日審訊，女警獲准繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告黃偉芬於今年10月10日，在秀茂坪商場內的惠康超級市場，偷竊兩盒珮氏驅蚊爽防蚊貼、一樽珮氏驅蚊爽噴霧、一樽李錦記XO醬及兩盒金嗓子喉片，總值234元。"},{"pid":"4e0a112b67fc1af833b0527e86a94c3723f08416","tid":38981,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf3a186fdce3bb6c3aa42998ce1ec74fc57e5ab","tid":38981,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f066c74a514cc52ed049acbec7402a01343995","tid":38981,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"2舊幾水都偷?唔怪得以前有人講如果識得個做公安嘅「朋友」,千其唔好帶佢去你屋企"},{"pid":"ed92b599608ed2d7fadd71ad9bac345c929aee6a","tid":38981,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2舊幾水都偷?唔怪得以前有人講如果識得個做公安嘅「朋友」,千其唔好帶佢去你屋企</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9a0f1710321e61aeb1cfb1f0681d6b89e80f57","tid":38981,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ddfcf79c5e00c9b5fe74e8fb7376298bfb8834","tid":38981,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T22:58:51.000Z","msg":"唔係休班？